@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ccqhec(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v1 - (wp.sin(v2 + 0.58) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.99)))
    v1 = 0.37
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.47)))
    v0 = v0
    v0 = 0.48
    v2 = 0.15
    data[tid] = v0
